{"sn35.97:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 35.97 ","sn35.97:0.2":"10. Salavagga ","sn35.97:0.3":"Pamadaviharisutta ","sn35.97:1.1":"“Pamadaviharinca vo, bhikkhave, desessami appamadaviharinca. ","sn35.97:1.2":"Tam sunatha. ","sn35.97:1.3":"Kathanca, bhikkhave, pamadavihari hoti? ","sn35.97:1.4":"Cakkhundriyam asamvutassa, bhikkhave, viharato cittam byasincati cakkhuvinneyyesu rupesu. ","sn35.97:1.5":"tassa byasittacittassa pamojjam na hoti. ","sn35.97:1.6":"Pamojje asati piti na hoti. ","sn35.97:1.7":"Pitiya asati passaddhi na hoti. ","sn35.97:1.8":"Passaddhiya asati dukkham hoti. ","sn35.97:1.9":"Dukkhino cittam na samadhiyati. ","sn35.97:1.10":"Asamahite citte dhamma na patubhavanti. ","sn35.97:1.11":"Dhammanam apatubhava pamadaviharitveva sankham gacchati …pe… ","sn35.97:1.12":"jivhindriyam asamvutassa, bhikkhave, viharato cittam byasincati jivhavinneyyesu rasesu, ","sn35.97:1.13":"tassa byasittacittassa …pe… ","sn35.97:1.14":"pamadaviharitveva sankham gacchati …pe… ","sn35.97:1.15":"manindriyam asamvutassa, bhikkhave, viharato cittam byasincati manovinneyyesu dhammesu, ","sn35.97:1.16":"tassa byasittacittassa pamojjam na hoti. ","sn35.97:1.17":"Pamojje asati piti na hoti. ","sn35.97:1.18":"Pitiya asati passaddhi na hoti. ","sn35.97:1.19":"Passaddhiya asati dukkham hoti. ","sn35.97:1.20":"Dukkhino cittam na samadhiyati. ","sn35.97:1.21":"Asamahite citte dhamma na patubhavanti. ","sn35.97:1.22":"Dhammanam apatubhava pamadaviharitveva sankham gacchati. ","sn35.97:1.23":"Evam kho, bhikkhave, pamadavihari hoti. ","sn35.97:2.1":"Kathanca, bhikkhave, appamadavihari hoti? ","sn35.97:2.2":"Cakkhundriyam samvutassa, bhikkhave, viharato cittam na byasincati cakkhuvinneyyesu rupesu, ","sn35.97:2.3":"tassa abyasittacittassa pamojjam jayati. ","sn35.97:2.4":"Pamuditassa piti jayati. ","sn35.97:2.5":"Pitimanassa kayo passambhati. ","sn35.97:2.6":"Passaddhakayo sukham viharati. ","sn35.97:2.7":"Sukhino cittam samadhiyati. ","sn35.97:2.8":"Samahite citte dhamma patubhavanti. ","sn35.97:2.9":"Dhammanam patubhava appamadaviharitveva sankham gacchati …pe… ","sn35.97:2.10":"jivhindriyam samvutassa, bhikkhave, viharato cittam na byasincati …pe… ","sn35.97:2.11":"appamadaviharitveva sankham gacchati. ","sn35.97:2.12":"Manindriyam samvutassa, bhikkhave, viharato cittam na byasincati, manovinneyyesu dhammesu, ","sn35.97:2.13":"tassa abyasittacittassa pamojjam jayati. ","sn35.97:2.14":"Pamuditassa piti jayati. ","sn35.97:2.15":"Pitimanassa kayo passambhati. ","sn35.97:2.16":"Passaddhakayo sukham viharati. ","sn35.97:2.17":"Sukhino cittam samadhiyati. ","sn35.97:2.18":"Samahite citte dhamma patubhavanti. ","sn35.97:2.19":"Dhammanam patubhava appamadaviharitveva sankham gacchati. ","sn35.97:2.20":"Evam kho, bhikkhave, appamadavihari hoti”ti. ","sn35.97:2.21":"Catuttham. "}